<solution>
<p><ul><li>1.06</li></ul></p><p>Because it does not matter which leg is a and which is b we call the missing leg x.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}^{{2}}+{7.52}^{{2}}={7.59}^{{2}}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}^{{2}}+{56.5504}={57.6081}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}^{{2}}={57.6081}-{56.5504}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}^{{2}}={1.0577}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle\sqrt{{{x}^{{2}}}}=\sqrt{{{1.0577}}}</m>.</p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}\approx{1.06}</m>.</p>
</solution>
